@startuml
!include https://raw.githubusercontent.com/proveo-ca/identity/main/proveo.puml
title Typed Execution-Events Ledger
' Ref:   Fowler, Event Sourcing — https://martinfowler.com/eaaDev/EventSourcing.html
' Ref:   Fowler, CQRS — https://martinfowler.com/bliki/CQRS.html
' Level: 4
' Provenance: projects/aphelion · session/store.go, types_runtime_records.go

component "Turn / tool / effect events"        as EV   <<async>>
database  "execution_events\nappend-only · monotonic seq" as LOG <<db>>
component "Projections\n(transcript · views)"   as PROJ <<app>>
actor     "Reader / audit"                      as R

EV   ARROW_QUEUE    LOG  : append (never mutate)
LOG  ARROW_MAIN     PROJ : replay / fold
PROJ ARROW_MAIN     R    : present
LOG  ARROW_OPTIONAL R    : canonical order

note bottom of LOG
  The **log is the truth**; the transcript is a *projection* of it.
  A monotonic per-session seq fixes execution order for audit & replay.
end note
@enduml
